name: EXPERIENCE_POOR_REASON
description:
Reasons why the QoE of the local user when receiving a remote audio stream is poor.Since
                v3.3.0

parameters.EXPERIENCE_REASON_NONE: 0: No reason, indicating a good QoE of the local user.

parameters.REMOTE_NETWORK_QUALITY_POOR: 1: The remote user's network quality is poor.

parameters.LOCAL_NETWORK_QUALITY_POOR: 2: The local user's network quality is poor.

parameters.WIRELESS_SIGNAL_POOR: 4: The local user's Wi-Fi or mobile network signal is weak.

parameters.WIFI_BLUETOOTH_COEXIST: 8: The local user enables both Wi-Fi and bluetooth, and their signals interfere with each other. As a result, audio transmission quality is undermined.
